Final Discworld novel will be called The Shepherd's Crown and feature witch Tiffany Aching who first appeared in The Wee Free Men in 2003 . 
  The book will be set in the fictional world of Discworld and will go on sale in September . 
  Sir Terry Pratchett died last month at the age of 66 . 
  He published his first book in 1983 and sold 85million books worldwide . 
 